  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/9a1bb14dc6fe4fe495348b89deb904c6.webp?t=1745571932\" width=310 height=35 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/447d09401705bf8b59a576f380f9b2db.poster.avif?t=1745571932\" width=616 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/447d09401705bf8b59a576f380f9b2db.webm?t=1745571932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/05e0d9969833555dcb30a8e0ad2c8047.webp?t=1745571932\" width=310 height=35 /></span><br>Your mysterious uncle left nothing but a letter in his wake, telling you to solve his final puzzle to obtain his heritage… but is there more to this than meets the eye?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/6c662ce5693429e855cdb9405a5f8524.webp?t=1745571932\" width=310 height=35 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/8eea4f403a89ad80a8dec234e490bcd0.poster.avif?t=1745571932\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/8eea4f403a89ad80a8dec234e490bcd0.webm?t=1745571932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/8eea4f403a89ad80a8dec234e490bcd0.mp4?t=1745571932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You will need to use your skills of deduction, combination, recollection and observation to overcome the various challenges in the game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/e62806c1bccbba6480df9ba9d3113d71.webp?t=1745571932\" width=310 height=35 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/e652bef5926fb92a88015e2491683f04.poster.avif?t=1745571932\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/e652bef5926fb92a88015e2491683f04.webm?t=1745571932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285080/extras/e652bef5926fb92a88015e2491683f04.mp4?t=1745571932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>While you wreck your brain on the puzzles don't forget to look around you, not everything is as simple as it seems!",
